<div class="row w-100 m-0" style="overflow: hidden">
	<div id="section-main" class="sermons-col-left bg-grey" style="width:100%">
		<h1 class="color-1a8090 bg-white text-center pb-2 pt-3 h2">第83屆 奮興會 第2講</h1>
		<article class="article pt-0 p-lg-5 pt-lg-0">
			<div class="article-meta">
				<span>
					<i class="fa fa-user"></i>
					講員：					<a href="/speaker/view/6">鮑維均牧師</a>
				</span>
				<span>
					<i class="fa fa-calendar-alt"></i>
					屆別:					<a href="/sermon/view?serial_no=83">第83屆</a>
				</span>
				<span data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="性質">
					<i class="fa fa-folder-open"></i>
					<a href="/sermon/view?serial_no=83#session-master-43">奮興會</a>
				</span>
			</div>
			<!--<div class="article-tag">
				<a href="#" class="badge">路加福音</a>
				<a href="#" class="badge">講道會</a>
				<a href="#" class="badge">56屆</a>
				<a href="#" class="badge">麥希真牧師</a>
			</div>-->
			<div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-4">
				<h2 class="article-title mb-0 h3">
					第二講  剛強壯膽				</h2>
									<a type="button" class="bookmark ms-3 " data-model="app\models\SessionMessage" data-model-id="802"></a>
							</div>
						<div class="article-content">
				
				<div class="h5 mb-4 d-md-flex justify-content-lg-between align-items-center">
					<div><span>經文：</span> 約書亞記  <a class="article-citation" href="javascript:void(0)" data-book="6" data-start-chapter="1" data-start-verse="1" data-end-verse="9">1:1-9</a></div><div><a href="javascript:void(0)" class="btn btn-danger btn-show-scripture text-center my-2 ml-auto align-self-start" style="display:none;">顯示經文</a>
				</div></div>				<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20">今天我們看第二個重要人物，摩西的繼承人約書<span style="letter-spacing:.1pt">亞。約書亞的就職禮非常特別，通常在一個人的就職禮上，我們會講到將要就職人的豐功偉績。但是約書亞書記一開始，正在約書亞的就職禮上，就用了摩西的名字十次，在神眼中，第一節『耶和華的僕人摩西死了以後，耶和華曉諭摩西的幫手，嫩的兒子約書亞</span><span style="letter-spacing:.15pt">說：』經文中，摩西是耶和華的僕人</span></span></span></span>&nbsp; <span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.1pt">--</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.15pt">&nbsp; 是特別的頭</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.05pt">銜，而約書亞是摩西的幫手</span></span></span></span>&nbsp; <span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.1pt">--</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.15pt">&nbsp; 摩西的僕人，這二句</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.1pt">話出現多次。『嫩的兒子約書亞，因為摩西曾按手在</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.05pt">他頭上，就被智慧的靈充滿</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.05pt">&hellip;&hellip;以後以色列中再沒有</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.3pt">興起先知像摩西的。』（申三十四：</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.3pt">9上，10上）是</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.1pt">約書亞就職禮的另外一版本，述說到約書亞做繼承人的一些事；換句話說，上一任的人絕對沒人能取代和</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20">與其比較的。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<h1 style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:14pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:&quot;BIZ UDPGothic&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">神為什麼揀選約書亞</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h1>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.55pt">記得在曠野去迦南探路的十二個探子回來後，</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">以色列人犯罪的事嗎？後來約書亞的同輩差不多都離世了，剩餘不多的同輩，但為什麼神揀選約書亞而不</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.55pt">揀選迦勒呢？民十三逐一介紹了去探路的十二個探</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">子，</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">16節，摩西將嫩的兒子何西阿改名為約書亞，在舊約，每次改名都預定有重要事情發生；25節『過了</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.05pt">四十天，他們窺探那地才回來。』十個探子都講負面</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">的話，惟有約書亞和迦勒講正面的話，但倆人中究竟誰是發言人？第一個說話的不是約書亞而是迦勒，</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">30節『迦勒在摩西面前安撫百姓，說：我們立刻上去得那地罷！我們足能得勝。』莫非迦勒比約書亞的地位</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.3pt">高？</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.65pt; margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.55pt">民十四形容同一個歷史時刻的片斷，有多次神</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">與摩西的對話，神終於寬恕以色列人，</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">20節『耶和華</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20">說：我照着你的話赦免了他們。』</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20">21,23節及24上<span style="letter-spacing:-.5pt">：</span><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">『然我指着我的永生起誓，遍地要被我的榮耀充滿。他們斷不得看見我向他們的祖宗所起誓應許之地。凡藐視我的，一個也不得看見；惟獨我的僕人迦勒，因他另有一個心志，專一跟從我，』奇怪嗎？講到「惟獨」迦勒是合神心意的，因為迦勒專心跟蹤神，還同摩西一樣被稱為神的僕人！</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.45pt; margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.05pt; margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<table style="border:undefined; width:100%">
	<tbody>
		<tr>
			<td>
			<div>
			<p style="margin-left:1.0pt"><span style="line-height:60%"><span style="font-size:8.5pt"><span style="line-height:60%"><span style="font-family:&quot;思源黑體 香港 Medium&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.9pt">一五</span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:8.5pt"><span style="line-height:60%"><span style="font-family:&quot;思源黑體 香港 Medium&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20">九</span></span></span></span></span></p>
			</div>
			</td>
		</tr>
	</tbody>
</table>

<p><span style="margin-left:589px; margin-top:444px; position:absolute; width:22px"><span style="z-index:15732736"><span style="height:55px"><img alt="Text Box: 一五九" class="shape" src="file:///C:/Users/Mr.Law/AppData/Local/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_image001.gif" style="height:44px; width:18px" /></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">如此看來，約書亞的地位不及上司，不及同輩！書二重點是要介紹喇合，因為差不多整卷書的神學宣言都是出自她的口！書二</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">:9喇合講到，『我知道耶和華已經把這地賜給你們，並且因你們的緣故我們都驚慌了。這地的一切居民，在你們面前心都消化了；』約書亞苦思苦想着怎樣攻城，想出用探子探路的錯誤方法，反而是這個外邦女子將最重要的神學宣言講出來。過了若干年後，以色列人回看，以為他們得到流奶與蜜之地，是因為他們的將軍夠聰明，但從第二章的神學預言中，清楚告訴我們，這與約書亞的戰術沒關係，而是當時最為人卑視的外邦人妓女喇合的口中</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.05pt">講出的重要宣言：神將這地賜給以色列人，這一戰術堅定了以色列人的信心。</span></span></span></span></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.25pt; margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">希伯來書十一章論述信心偉人因着信做了的事；講完摩西後本應講約書亞，因為從某一層面來說，約書亞地位應比摩西高，因為有的事摩西做不到，而約書亞做到了！摩西不能進迦南，是約書亞帶領以色列民進入流奶與蜜之地，約書亞成全了亞伯拉罕的約；神應許給亞伯拉罕的地，終於在約書亞時代成就了。</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt"> 29節，以色列人過紅海，30節，『以色列人因着信，圍繞耶利哥城七日，城牆就倒塌了。』原文聖經在此</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.6pt">說：『因着信，城牆無端端倒下了！』</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.6pt">31</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.3pt">節又說，</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">『妓女喇合因着信，曾和和平平的接待探子，就不與那些不順從的人一同滅亡。』在信心偉人的篇幅中，為什麼對約書亞隻字不題？根據來十一，約書亞連他</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20">的敵人都比不上 。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.3pt; margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.05pt; margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">書一：</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">2,3,6中，「賜給」這動詞不停出現，原來中心思想與第二章一樣：這地耶和華賜給你們了。神為甚麼揀選約書亞呢？除了順服之外，其餘不知道。</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.55pt">約書亞記的中心不在約書亞，而是耶和華自己的工</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">作！「當剛強壯膽」這句話多次出現，在約書亞身上用了十三次，在摩西身上用了兩次，是否因為約書亞膽小害怕？抑或敵人太厲害？</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.25pt; margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<h1 style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:14pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:&quot;BIZ UDPGothic&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">剛強壯膽的真正涵義</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h1>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.5pt">書一：</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.5pt">6、9</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.45pt">臨打仗前講神的安慰，正如我們考</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.05pt">試前、見工前，甚至談戀愛前，視乎自己有多少成把</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.1pt">握，必定交托給神一樣。作為一個基督徒，每次不行時我都會祈禱，你考試前不停禱告能做得到，但考試後都能不停禱告就難做得到！請問，是進去打仗得到神應許的那地難些，還是，求神給我勇氣去謹守遵循神的話語難些？哪一樣需要更多的勇氣、需要剛強壯膽？<strong>約曾書亞記中，惟一未知之數不是戰爭的結果，</strong></span></span></span></span><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20">而是勝利之後仍對神至死不渝的忠心！</span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.25pt; margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.65pt">到底何時需要剛強壯膽呢？我們來看約書亞的</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.3pt">臨終遺言</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.3pt">(書二十三：1-5</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20">)</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.2pt">。神所剪除，鏟除的都做</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.35pt">了。</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.35pt">6</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.35pt">節：『所以你們要大大壯膽，謹守遵行寫在摩</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.4pt">西律法書上的一切話，不可偏離左右。』</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.4pt">7</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.4pt">-</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.4pt">8</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.25pt">節，與</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.1pt">他們的國民住在一起時，不可敬拜他們的神，只要敬拜耶和華獨一真神。其實，約書亞記中講的「剛強壯</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20">膽」，是指：要守律法，對神忠心。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.55pt; margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.05pt; margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">患難時依靠上帝不難，吃得好，住得好時要依靠上帝就難得多；我有一對很熟悉的夫婦朋友，九三年他太太懷孕時，患了肺炎，惟有將腹中孩子取出，感謝神，胎兒可以生存，但媽媽就危險了，這姊妹在休克狀態中過了一個半個月，醫生說，只有看神怎樣做了，結果神奇妙地醫好她。也就是那年暑假，我太太患上了癌症，年尾離世。兩三年後，我們再講起這些事，我問：究竟是困難時親近神容易些，抑或是安泰時親近神容易些？以我的經歷，我發現一九九八年幸福的日子依靠上帝，實在難過一九九三年在艱難中依靠上帝！困難時，基督徒都懂祈禱，但困難過去，好</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20">吃好住的日子，依靠神真的是很難</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"> !</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.05pt; margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.05pt; margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.55pt">書一和申三十四是約書亞登基的二個版本；申</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">三十一是第三個版本，講述神任命約書亞繼承摩西的職事。請看第</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">19節：『現在你要寫一篇歌，教導以色列人，傳給他們，使這歌見證他的不是。』為什麼神要在這裡責備以色列人呢？20節『因為我將他們領進我向他們列祖起誓應許那流奶與蜜之地，他們在那裏喫得飽足，身體肥胖，就必偏向別神事奉它們，藐視我，背棄我的約。』在安泰的日子裏就去拜別神，困難打仗時依靠耶和華，進入流奶與蜜之地之後，那才是靈性上艱難的日子。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.45pt; margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">我們今天是處順境抑或逆境？也許你正處於流奶與蜜之地的光景，你正在敬拜別神還是敬拜真神呢？我們是否吃得飽足，身體肥胖就轉眼望其它事呢？我們遇難處會晝夜流淚祈禱，順境時我們有多少次晝夜祈禱呢？真正的挑戰是在一切平穩順利時！</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.65pt; margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">我們當剛強壯膽依靠上帝，謹守遵循摩西律法上一切話語。每一場勝仗之後，都令到以色列進入更危險境況；原以為打贏仗是好事，且每一仗都令他們更近流奶與蜜之地，但現在問題是，他們會不會在此安樂時刻才全軍覆滅！</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.6pt; margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.55pt">如果我們從小一直信靠神，神聽禱告，正如以</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">色列人每次打仗都祈禱一樣，當我們有了想要的一切之後，就忘記敬拜神，這是最可憐的事！是神令我們</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20">贏了這麼多場仗，我們反而輸了最後一場</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"> -- 唯一一<span style="letter-spacing:-.05pt">場重要的戰爭！我們高興神垂聽禱告呢，還是吃得飽</span><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">足，就轉眼敬拜假神？甚麼時候需剛強壯膽呢？不是打仗時，而是太平年間。在以為沒仗打時，撒旦會趁機破壞我們的生命。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.1pt; margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<h1 style="margin-top:.05pt; margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:14pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:&quot;BIZ UDPGothic&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.05pt">神為甚麼要大用約書亞</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h1>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.1pt; margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">約書亞究竟做了甚麼值得記念，值得作者稱讚？請看書二十四：</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">31『約書亞在世和約書亞死後，那些知道耶和華為以色列人所行諸事的長老還在的時候，以色列人事奉耶和華。』這是聖經裏最偉大歌頌約書亞的句子，約書亞在世和離世，所有跟從他的人敬畏耶和華。士師基甸，上半生有美好的戰爭，神與他同在，但他下半生卻造偶像，他建造的以弗得成為以色列眾人的網羅。基甸死後，人敬拜偶像，而約書亞死後，以色列人事奉耶和華，這就是基甸與約書亞根本</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.2pt">不同。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.45pt; margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">約書亞在世時和離世時，人都敬拜事奉耶和華。</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.55pt">我有位同事去了蘇丹回來，他見到一個墓碑，是一</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">位西方醫生去蘇丹做醫療宣教工作，為着傳福音給一位婦女而喪生了自己寶貴的生命；那婦女的丈夫很惱怒，去到醫院將他殺了，醫生死後，人們去他住處看他留下甚麼遺產，原來他死前已將一切分給窮人，最後人們在他墓碑上寫下：他愛神！我同事將照相片給我看：墓碑上寫着，他愛神！我們離世之後，希望別人在我們的墓碑寫上甚麼字呢？</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.45pt; margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.05pt; margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.6pt">跟隨他的人敬畏耶和華，這就是約書的貢獻。</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">神呼召約書亞，不是做所謂的「大事」，不是做大將軍，而是要他令到身邊的人，在世離世時都敬畏耶和華！我們是否敬畏耶和華的群體？如果神今天將我們接回天家，會不會是在歷史長卷中揭去一頁，完全不</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.55pt">關緊要，絲毫不受影響？你生存，周圍人的如此，</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20">你不存在，周圍的人也如此，沒有任何影響</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20">? 要是神<span style="letter-spacing:.55pt">說，這個人在世和離世之後，他身邊的人敬畏耶和</span><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">華，這也是神對約書亞的評價，你想得到嗎？</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.55pt; margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.4pt">今晚我發出兩個呼召，１</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.4pt">.</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.35pt">我們是否在好吃好住</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">的環境下敬拜別神？是否多次的勝仗，神多次垂聽我們的禱告反而成為我們的陷阱？我們是否這麼可憐？如果是的話，我們要剛強壯膽。２</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">.生命的長短在神手中，我們是否願意用我們餘下的日子，改變自己和周圍的人，我們改變不了，是神來改變，但我們是否願意成為神手中的器皿？</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.55pt; margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.6pt">幾個星期前，芝加哥有個大會，提到一個異像</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.1pt; margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20">-- 「三一運動」，呼籲在職人士將三分之一時間交給<span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">主；神給了你許多不同的福氣，此刻，將你寶貴的时間交給上帝三分之一，你願意嗎？二週前我去澳洲講道，有位老姊妹對我講：我想我不能有「三一」了，但我願將我遺產三分之一獻上，為主所用，以致你們</span>的「三一運動」能延續&hellip;&hellip; 我們是老年力衺，以遺<span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">產獻給主，還是年輕力壯，以年輕的生命力，還有三分之一時間為主？神要興起中學生、大學生奉獻，神要興起最有能力、最有經驗、最有生命力的生命作出奉獻，神用得着我們，願意做今天的約書亞嗎？</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.1pt; margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.1pt; margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20">在世、離世都忠於耶和<span style="letter-spacing:-.5pt">華</span></span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.6pt; margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.15pt">當我們被主接去之後，願人們這樣懷緬</span></span></span></span>&nbsp; <span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.1pt">--</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.15pt">&nbsp; 他在</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.1pt">世、離世都忠於耶和華，或者有後人在墓碑上為我們寫上：他愛神！又或者將來我們的墓碑上寫着，他有</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.45pt">學位、有名車、有最好的名牌等等</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.45pt">!我們想有甚麼樣</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:.1pt">的墓碑？願意我們剛強壯膽，回應神的呼召。神給我們很多恩典，我們願意敬拜獨一真神，不願敬拜鄰居的別神，如果有弟兄姊妹願意回轉，願意剛強壯膽敬</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20">拜神，請起立決志。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.5pt; margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">不要讓神多年垂聽你禱告成為陷阱，沒有人知道餘下的日子有多長；可能幾個月，可能幾十年，如果神今天給你機會，你願改變方向，全時間成為神的工人嗎？以致你在世和離世時，人家見到你就感謝敬拜神，有這樣的兄姊，請走到台前向神立志，在神和人面前宣告你公開的志願。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:.6pt; margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:新細明體,serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:#231f20"><span style="letter-spacing:-.1pt">可能你等這一刻等了一年，也許等了二十年，神今天要你做決定，不要攔阻神的工作，今天就出來，回應神的呼召，改變沒意義的人生，今天神要用你，不是因你有多能幹，有才華，皆因神要在祂子民中工作，請走出來，為你禱告。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
				
				<br>
				<p class="h5">
					<span>講員：</span> 鮑維均牧師
					<br>
					<span>傳譯：</span> 周志豪牧師
				</p>			</div>
			<div class="article-navigation d-flex justify-content-between mt-5">
